Name: Firebowl / Fire Pit
Description:
The Outland Firebowl has the sentiment of a traditional campfire, without the tireless back bending and fabric clinging smoke! Adding an authentic ambience to any atmosphere, the Outland Firebowl Deluxe is portable and convenient.

As it is CSA approved and unthreatening towards most burn bans, feel free to pack up the Outland Firebowl Deluxe in your RV and hit the road for camping! With construction from high quality steel and a protective enamel finish, your Outland is guaranteed for long lasting durability.

Not a camper? Not a problem. The Outland Firebowl Deluxe can be used in the backyard, patio or porch. Burning clean and smokeless, our Firebowls provide instant warmth and a genuine campfire experience anywhere you go.

Name: Queen Air Mattress
Description:
http://www.soundasleepproducts.com/products

SoundAsleep Products has spent years developing the highest quality air mattresses on the market. Our first product, The SoundAsleep Dream Series with ComfortCoil Technology was released in mid 2013. Over a dozen additional products are in development and will be released over the coming quarters.

The SoundAsleep Dream Series with ComfortCoil Technology comes available as a queen sized, "double - raised" mattress. The air mattresses measures 78x58x19 inches with the look and feel of a traditional queen sized mattress and box spring.

The soft top flocking offers breathability and water proofing to the mattress and prevents penetration from spills or sweat. The 19" height provides that extra height and support you can expect from a SoundAsleep Product. The patented motor was built for simplicity. Users turn the knob clockwise to inflate the mattress and then back to center when the air mattress has reached the desired firmness. A counterclockwise turn will deflate the mattress.

The Dream Series was designed as an inhome product; perfect for the occasional overnight guest or when the in-laws come over for a visit. The mattress is not designed for every day use in place of a traditional bed. Every day use will degrade the mattress and this type of use is not covered under the warranty.

Name: Concrete Mixer
Description:
This concrete mixer successfully mixes:

  • two (2) 70 lb. bags of concrete and water at a time, or
  • three (3) 50 lb. bags of concrete and water at a time
If it's over-filled, the mixer has a safety feature that will automatically shut it off. If auto shut off occurs:

  1. Empty the mixer
  2. Press the red reset button

Separately, there is a grease fitting on the bottom that requires a refill of grease from a grease dispenser every ten (10) hours of operation in order to keep the mixer freely rotating properly. Without this grease, the mixer will freeze up and stop rotating properly. Borrow an available grease dispenser with this mixer, or borrow/rent one from a local mechanic if none are available.

Name: Air Mattress, Queen
Description:
http://www.soundasleepproducts.com/products

SoundAsleep Products has spent years developing the highest quality air mattresses on the market. Our first product, The SoundAsleep Dream Series with ComfortCoil Technology was released in mid 2013. Over a dozen additional products are in development and will be released over the coming quarters.

The SoundAsleep Dream Series with ComfortCoil Technology comes available as a queen sized, "double - raised" mattress. The air mattresses measures 78x58x19 inches with the look and feel of a traditional queen sized mattress and box spring.

The soft top flocking offers breathability and water proofing to the mattress and prevents penetration from spills or sweat. The 19" height provides that extra height and support you can expect from a SoundAsleep Product. The patented motor was built for simplicity. Users turn the knob clockwise to inflate the mattress and then back to center when the air mattress has reached the desired firmness. A counterclockwise turn will deflate the mattress.

The Dream Series was designed as an inhome product; perfect for the occasional overnight guest or when the in-laws come over for a visit. The mattress is not designed for every day use in place of a traditional bed. Every day use will degrade the mattress and this type of use is not covered under the warranty.
